                    -FOG/GAM.013

        First Osborne Group (FOG) Games Disk

This disk contains support files for the Adventure 
game AD.COM found on -FOG/GAM.014.  This version was 
received from the Osborne Users Group (OUG) of the 
Washington D.C. area.

To play Adventure, make a copy of this disk and 
SYSGEN system tracks to the copy.  Place AD.COM in 
drive B and the copy of this disk in drive A.  At 
the A> prompt, type
     B:AD
This Adventure game is similar but more detailed 
than Adventure found on -FOG/GAM.001.  In 
particular, you can interrupt a game for 
continuation at a later time.  To interrupt play, 
use the SAVE verb.  When the A> prompt appears, type
     <CTRL-C>
     SAVE 157 B:ADSAVE.COM
B must have at least 40K space.  To restart the 
game, at the A> prompt, type
     B:ADSAVE
See ADVENTUR.DOC for further information.

